Hey!

327
00:14:55,510 --> 00:14:56,869
I was using the toilet!

328
00:14:56,870 --> 00:14:58,469
My mom was right.

329
00:14:58,470 --> 00:15:00,100
That phone's your real wife.

330
00:15:02,510 --> 00:15:03,740
What are you looking for?

331
00:15:04,390 --> 00:15:05,890
It's your dad, Shen Qing.

332
00:15:06,200 --> 00:15:08,059
I burned my hand
shutting off the stove for him,

333
00:15:08,060 --> 00:15:09,349
and he didn't even notice!

334
00:15:09,350 --> 00:15:10,930
He even asked me where I got burned!

335
00:15:11,510 --> 00:15:13,899
You'd at least notice if a working animal

336
00:15:13,900 --> 00:15:15,890
on your farm got injured!

337
00:15:16,280 --> 00:15:18,029
Ignoring something
and being completely unaware

338
00:15:18,030 --> 00:15:19,410
are two different things.

339
00:15:19,470 --> 00:15:20,539
My dad is old.

340
00:15:20,540 --> 00:15:21,299
He's slow to react.

341
00:15:21,300 --> 00:15:22,580
He genuinely didn't know.

342
00:15:22,990 --> 00:15:24,460
Slow to react?

343
00:15:24,620 --> 00:15:26,939
