356
00:15:48,579 --> 00:15:49,450
He did that just now.

357
00:15:49,910 --> 00:15:50,580
Found it.

358
00:15:51,430 --> 00:15:53,029
Close the door!

359
00:15:53,030 --> 00:15:54,260
Enjoy your phone!

360
00:16:00,140 --> 00:16:01,060
Mom.

361
00:16:01,670 --> 00:16:02,909
You're not getting any younger.

362
00:16:02,910 --> 00:16:04,410
Can you take it easy?

363
00:16:05,230 --> 00:16:06,210
Take it easy?

364
00:16:06,470 --> 00:16:07,650
How?

365
00:16:09,230 --> 00:16:10,579
All these household chores.

366
00:16:10,580 --> 00:16:11,930
This huge mess to handle.

367
00:16:12,190 --> 00:16:14,299
