is going to get snatched away.

380
00:16:39,540 --> 00:16:40,380
Mom.

381
00:16:40,580 --> 00:16:41,890
Thank you, but don't get involved.

382
00:16:42,300 --> 00:16:44,580
Go home, rest, dance.
Wouldn't that be nice?

383
00:16:44,670 --> 00:16:45,949
Go home and dance?

384
