00:21:30,820 --> 00:21:32,380
Slow down!

535
00:22:19,100 --> 00:22:20,100
Zhuoran?

536
00:22:20,820 --> 00:22:21,780
Zhuoran?

537
00:22:22,580 --> 00:22:23,730
Where is he?

538
00:22:28,270 --> 00:22:29,300
Zhuoran!

