548
00:22:47,060 --> 00:22:48,380
If he were my husband...

549
00:22:51,820 --> 00:22:52,890
Gosh, this man...

550
00:22:55,580 --> 00:22:58,260
If he were my husband,
I'd break his legs.

551
00:22:58,910 --> 00:23:00,300
Crazy man!

552
00:23:49,190 --> 00:23:50,130
Ms. Nie.

553
00:23:52,540 --> 00:23:54,130
Of course, I knew it was you.

554
00:23:54,270 --> 00:23:55,820
You're always on Beijing time.

555
00:23:57,100 --> 00:23:59,820
I always call at the exact same time.

556
00:24:00,060 --> 00:24:01,930
How could I be late?

557
00:24:04,620 --> 00:24:05,450
Guess

558
00:24:05,910 --> 00:24:07,170
