956
00:42:20,220 --> 00:42:22,050
This is so pretty!

957
00:42:24,950 --> 00:42:26,930
I wonder

958
00:42:27,140 --> 00:42:28,700
what she looks like.

959
00:42:28,830 --> 00:42:31,010
No idea. I've never seen her.

960
00:42:31,790 --> 00:42:33,490
We call her a fairy for a reason.

961
00:42:39,330 --> 00:42:41,880
(Addressed to Shen Zhuoran,
Drum Tower District, Nanjing, Jiangsu)

962
00:42:43,350 --> 00:42:44,139
Look at this.

963
00:42:44,140 --> 00:42:45,480
Look at the address.

964
00:42:45,480 --> 00:42:46,225
Nie Juanjuan.

965
00:42:46,226 --> 00:42:48,120
