237 Yihe Road, Nanjing)

966
00:42:48,310 --> 00:42:50,740
237 Yihe Road.

967
00:42:51,260 --> 00:42:52,300
Odd.

968
00:42:52,390 --> 00:42:53,490
Just a mailbox.

969
00:42:53,620 --> 00:42:55,890
No specific home address.

970
00:42:56,260 --> 00:42:56,890
Come on.

971
00:42:56,950 --> 00:42:58,340
Let's see this "fairy" in person.

972
00:42:59,030 --> 00:43:00,139
See her in person?

973
00:43:00,140 --> 00:43:00,989
Yes.

974
00:43:00,990 --> 00:43:01,890
Let's go!

975
